All India Institute of Medical Sciences Bhopal (AIIMS Bhopal) is one of the seven apex healthcare institutes set up in India by the Ministry of Healthcare and Family Welfare (MHFW) under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojana (PMSSY). All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Bhubaneswar

All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Bhubaneswar is one of the apex healthcare Institutes established by the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare, Government of India under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojna (PMSSY). All India Institute of Medical Sciences, Bhubaneswar was established as an autonomous institution and institute of National importance through the All India Institute of Medical Sciences.

AIIMS Jodhpur

AIIMS Jodhpur is one of the six AIIMS institutes established under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojna (PMSSY) by the Ministry of Health & Family Welfare, Government of India. Established by an Act of Parliament, it is a medical research public university as well as a medical college offering medical education, nursing and paramedical training to students. As one of the premier medical colleges in Rajasthan.

AIIMS Patna

The All India Institute of Medical Sciences Patna (AIIMS Patna), previously known as Jaya Prakash Narayan All India Institute of Medical Sciences (JPNAIIMS), is one of the six institutes established under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojana (PMSSY). AIIMS Patna was established in the year 2012. It is an autonomous institute registered under the Indian Societies Registration Act.

AIIMS Raipur

AIIMS Raipur is an autonomous institute which was established in 2012. The institute is located in Raipur, Chhattisgarh and is easily accessible to those residing in central India. AIIMS Raipur is one of the six institutes which were set up under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojna (PMSSY). It is registered under the Indian Societies Registration Act which gives it the autonomous status

AIIMS Rishikesh

AIIMS Rishikesh is one of the six institutes set up by the Government of India under the Pradhan Mantri Swasthya Suraksha Yojna (PMSSY). Established in the year 2012, AIIMS Rishikesh is an autonomous institute registered under the Indian Societies Registration Act.
